maven-tree - maven dependency tree graph builder

1) Overview
2) Requirements
3) Usage
4) License


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Overview

maven-tree recurses through your maven projects and generates a graph
from the declared dependencies.

The generated dependencies file is in the GraphML format
(http://graphml.graphdrawing.org/) and can be viewed / analyzed with
applications like Gephi (http://gephi.github.io/). Gephi allows you to
visualize the graph and calculate common graph metrics like for example
the degree of edges or nodes.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Requirements

maven-tree require the pygraphml python module. Install pygraphml like
this:

$ git clone https://github.com/hadim/pygraphml.git
$ cd pygraphml/
$ pip install .


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage

$ python maven-tree.py output.graphml path/to/maven_dirs

For more options see:
$ python maven-tree.py --help


